'SURROUND' IS A GAME YOU CAN PLAYAGAINST THE APPLE. YOU EACH SPEEDAROUND THE LO-RES GRAPHICS SCREEN;THE APPLE STARTING ON THE LEFT ANDYOU STARTING ON THE RIGHT. THEOBJECT ISTO GET THE OTHER PLAYER TO CRASHINTO A WALL. USE THE NUMBERS ON THENUMBER PAD TO STEER. YOU CAN TRAVELUP; DOWN; LEFT; RIGHT; ANDDIAGONALLY.NOTE: LAPTOP NUMBER PADS MAY NOTWORK WITH THIS GAME.